DG.plugin.Sampler.about.item2: Collect <n> samples controls how many samples to repeat in a given experiment.
DG.plugin.Sampler.about.paragraph2.1: The speed of sampling can be controlled, as well as whether to sample with or without replacement (in Options tab). The data generated from the Sampler will appear in a hierarchical table. The top level represents the experiment (one complete run of a simulation) and allows you to compute statistics about an entire experiment.
